Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper proposes an algorithm for fault management in an outdoor cellular network, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed algorithm uses deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The use of deep reinforcement learning in the proposed algorithm also falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the use of the proposed algorithm for self-healing of the cellular network cluster, which can be considered as a control system. 
5. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the improvement of the downlink signal to interference plus noise ratio, which is related to information theory.
